<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span style="color:#008000">(١٠٨١ - ١١٤٥ هـ)</span> <span style="color:#008000">(١٦٧٠ - ١٧٣٢ م)</span><a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
